          <p>1-on-1 sessions on Python, Django, game dev with Godot, and more. Custom lessons, code reviews, and flexible scheduling.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <a href="/services/python-tutoring" class="btn btn-neutral">Learn More</a>
            <a href="sms:+14042134870?body=BOOK%20TUTORING" class="btn btn-secondary ml-2">Book Session</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-primary shadow-xl min-h-64">
        <div class="card-body">
